org.apache.olingo.server.sample.processor

Class CarsProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.olingo.server.sample.processor.CarsProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.ComplexProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.EntityCollectionProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.EntityProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.PrimitiveProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.PrimitiveValueProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.Processor

    public class CarsProcessor
extends Object
implements org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.EntityCollectionProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.EntityProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.PrimitiveProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.PrimitiveValueProcessor, org.apache.olingo.server.api.processor.ComplexProcessor
    This processor will deliver entity collections, single entities as well as properties of an entity. This is a very simple example which should give you a rough guideline on how to implement such an processor. See the JavaDoc of the server.api interfaces for more information.
